Speed-extreme proposal: the asymptotically fastest / best constant-factor / early-exit
solution, accepted even if it uses more memory.

Replace this file with the implementation and rename it with the selected language
extension. Choose the language by performance analysis for raw runtime (e.g. C++, C, Rust).

If this proposal would coincide with the recommended solution.{ext} (a Pareto-optimal
problem where the fast + lean solution is also the fastest), do not create this file at
all - keep only solution.{ext} and explain in notes.md. Add this file only when the
speed extreme is a genuinely different, non-dominated solution.
